skill.name: Piltover Pulverizer
skill.desc:
Vi shield herself and deals magic damage to her target and enemies behind it.

On her 2nd cast, she also dashes through her target.

On her 3rd cast, she instead throws her target into the air and slams them back to the ground, dealing in a circle around her target.

skill.name: Orbs of Deception
skill.desc: Ahri fires an orb in a 5 hex line, dealing magic damage to all enemies it passes through on the way out and the way back. Enemies already hit by an orb take 60% damage for each subsequent orb. Ahri fires additional orb(s) for each time she has cast this combat.

skill.name: Pulverize
skill.desc: Alistar charges at his target, knocking them back for a short distance. Then he slams the ground, dealing magic damage and stunning all nearby enemies for a few seconds.

skill.name: Volley
skill.desc: Ashe fires a volley of 8 arrows centered on her target, dealing physical damage per arrow and slowing their Attack Speed by 20% for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Rocket Grab
skill.desc: Blitzcrank pulls the farthest enemy, dealing magic damage and stunning them for 1.5 seconds. His next attack knocks them up for 1 second. Allies within range will prefer attacking Blitzcrank's target.

skill.name: Sear
skill.desc:
Brand launches a fireball at the nearest enemy, lighting them ablaze for 4 seconds and dealing magic damage. If the enemy is already on fire, they take bonus magic damage which stuns them for a few seconds.

VIP Bonus: Brand fires a 2nd fireball at a different nearby target (priortizes ablaze enemies) dealing 45% reduced damage.

skill.name: Vault Breaker
skill.desc: Braum slams his vault door into the ground, creating a fissure towards his target. Enemies within 2 hexes of Braum, and those struck by the fissure, are stunned for a few seconds and take magic damage.

skill.name: Ace in the Hole
skill.desc: Caitlyn takes aim at the farthest enemy, firing a deadly bullet towards them that deals magic damage to the first enemy it hits.

skill.name: Defensive Sweep
skill.desc: Camille gains a shield blocking damage over 4 seconds, then sweeps her leg, dealing magic damage to enemies in a cone. While this shield holds, Camille's attacks restore Health.

skill.name: Feast
skill.desc: Cho’Gath devours the lowest Health enemy within range, dealing magic damage. If this kills the target, Cho’Gath gains a stack of Feast (increased to two in Hyper Roll), up to max stacks. Each stack of Feast permanently grants 2% bonus Health and size.

skill.name: Bombardment
skill.desc: Corki fires a missile at his target that explodes on impact, dealing magic damage to enemies within 1 hex.

skill.name: Decimate
skill.desc: Darius swings his axe in a circle, dealing  magic damage, then heals himself for each enemy hit.

skill.name: Spinning Axes
skill.desc:
Passive: Draven ignores 25% of his target's Armor.

Draven starts spinning an axe, empowering his next attack to deal % of his Attack Damage plus bonus physical damage. It will return to his original location after striking the target. If Draven catches it, he will empower the axe again. Draven can spin up to 2 axes at a time.

VIP Bonus: Draven gains infinite attack range and ignores 25% his target's Armor.

skill.name: Parallel Convergence
skill.desc: Ekko invokes an afterimage that bats a device towards the largest group of units. Upon landing, it deals magic damage to enemies within and applies reduced Attack Speed for 4 seconds. Allies inside gain bonus Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Mystic Shot
skill.desc: Ezreal fires a missile at his target, dealing 150% of his Attack Damage plus bonus physical damage. If the missile hits, he grants himself 18% bonus stacking Attack Speed, up to 100% at 5 stacks.

skill.name: Colossal Entrance
skill.desc:
Galio becomes invulnerable and leaps into the sky before crashing down on the largest group of enemies. Enemies within a large radius take magic damage and are knocked up.

Passive: Galio's Critical Strikes slam the ground, dealing bonus magic damage to enemies around his target.

skill.name: Parrrley
skill.desc: Gangplank attacks his target with his gun, dealing 170% of his Attack Damage plus bonus physical damage. If this attack kills a champion, Gangplank plunders 1 gold.

skill.name: GNAR!
skill.desc:
Gnar transforms into Mega Gnar for the rest of combat. Mega Gnar throws a boulder at the farthest enemy within 3 hexes, dealing % of his Attack Damage plus bonus damage as physical damage to all enemies it passes through.

While in Mega Gnar form. Gnar is melee, gains Health, and his mana costs are reduced by 20.

skill.name: Harsh Lesson
skill.desc: Illaoi slams her target, linking her soul to it for 5 seconds and dealing magic damage. While linked, Illaoi is healed for % of the damage taken by her target.

skill.name: Bladesurge
skill.desc: Irelia dashes to her target, striking them for physical damage. If this kills the target, she Bladesurges again at the lowest Health enemy.

skill.name: Ageless Standard
skill.desc: Jarvan calls down his standard to a nearby location, granting all nearby allies within 3 hexes Attack Speed for 5 seconds.

skill.name: To the Skies! / Shock Blast
skill.desc:
To the Skies!: Jayce overcharges himself, becoming unstoppable and gaining a shield for 3 seconds. Jayce then attacks twice, cleaving enemies in front of him for % of his Attack Damage as physical damage before leaping to the skies and slamming down on his target. Enemies within 2 hexes take the same damage and suffer a % reduction in Armor and Magic Resist for 5 seconds.

Passive: Jayce gains 40 Armor and Magic Resist.
------------------------------------
Shock Blast: Jayce summons an acceleration gate, granting allies within the same row % Attack Speed for 5 seconds. He then replaces his next 3 attacks with orbs of electricity that deal % of his Attack Damage as physical damage in a 1 hex area around his target. The 3rd orb has a larger 2 hex area of effect.

Passive: Jayce's range is increased by 4 hexes and he gains Attack Damage.

skill.name: Curtain Call
skill.desc:
Jhin transforms his weapon into a powerful sniper rifle for his next 4 shots. Each shot deals % of his Attack Damage as physical damage, reduced by 33% for each target it pierces through. The 4th shot is guaranteed to critically strike, and deals 100% more damage based on his target's missing Health.

Passive: Jhin always attacks fixed times per second. He converts each 1% of bonus Attack Speed into 0.8 Attack Damage.

skill.name: Super Mega Death Rocket
skill.desc:
Jinx rides her rocket into the sky, then comes crashing down near the center-most enemy, dealing magic damage to enemies around the epicenter, and 50% to all other enemies in in a large area. The epicenter burns every unit except Jinx for 5 seconds, dealing % of the target's maximum Health as true damage, and reducing healing by 50% for the duration.

She then swaps to her rocket launcher and targets random units for the rest of combat. Her attacks now explode for % of her Attack Damage as physical damage in a small area around her target.

skill.name: Icathian Monsoon
skill.desc:
Kai’sa dashes away from all enemies, then fires a volley of missiles spread evenly among all enemies that deal magic damage each.

For each time Kai'Sa has attacked this combat, she'll fire an additional missile.

skill.name: Null Sphere
skill.desc: Kassadin fires an orb of void energy at his target, dealing magic damage. Enemies hit by the orb suffer a increased Mana cost for their next Ability cast. Kassadin also grants himself a shield and take 25% less damage for 5 seconds.

skill.name: Void Assault
skill.desc: Kha'Zix leaps towards the lowest Health enemy. striking them as physical damage and increasing their maximum Mana by 50% until they cast.

skill.name: Solar Eclipse
skill.desc:
Leona calls down a beacon of light upon herself, granting herself a shield for a few seconds. Leona and allies within 2 hexes gain Armor and Magic Resistance for the same duration.

VIP Bonus: Every second, Leona heals herself for 1.25% of max health for each unit targeting her.

skill.name: Relentless Pursuit
skill.desc: Lucian dashes away from his current target and fires shots at nearby enemies that each deal magic damage.

skill.name: Wild Growth
skill.desc: Lulu enlarges low Health allies, granting them bonus Health and knocking up enemies near them. If the ally is already enlarged, they are healed instead.

skill.name: Malefic Visions
skill.desc:
Malzahar infects the mind of the closest unafflicted target, dealing magic damage over 8 seconds and reducing the Magic Resist of enemies by 40%.

If an afflicted target dies, Malefic Visions spreads to the nearest unafflicted targets with the remaining duration.

skill.name: Make it Rain
skill.desc: Miss Fortune rains 4 waves of bullets down around her target, dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and reducing their incoming healing by 50% for 6 seconds.

skill.name: Soul Shackles
skill.desc:
Morgana grants herself a shield for 3 seconds and shackles herself to all enemies in a 2 hex radius. She then deals magic damage per second to them, as long as the shield holds.

If the shield expires without being broken, all targets are stunned for a few seconds. If the shield is broken, Morgana instead refunds herself 30 mana.

skill.name: Unspeakable Horror
skill.desc: Nocturne terrifies his target, stunning them with fear for a few seconds and dealing magic damage over the duration.

skill.name: Command: Shockwave
skill.desc: Orianna sends her ball towards the largest group of champions, then commands it to release a shockwave. Allies within 2 hexes gain shield for 4 seconds, while enemies within the area are briefly knocked up and dealt magic damage. Enemies adjacent to the ball are drawn in and stunned.

skill.name: Buckler Toss
skill.desc: Poppy throws her buckler at the farthest enemy, dealing % of her Armor as magic damage. The buckler then bounces back, granting Poppy a shield that blocks damage.

skill.name: Disarming Assault
skill.desc: Quinn sends Valor out at the target with the highest Attack Speed, dealing magic damage to the target and nearby enemies, disarming them for a few seconds.

skill.name: Furious Bite
skill.desc: Rek'Sai bites her target, dealing 125% of her Attack Damage plus bonus damage as physical damage and healing herself. If she has already bit her target, she heals more instead.

skill.name: Toxic Wave
skill.desc: Renata unleashes a toxic poison wave towards the largest group of nearby enemies within 6 hexes, poisoning all enemies caught in its path for 15 seconds. Poisoned enemies suffer 20% reduced Attack Speed and take magic damage per second. Damage dealt by the poison can stack.

skill.name: Fury of the North
skill.desc: Sejuani signals Bristle to charge, dealing magic damage and stunning her target for a few seconds. She then gains Frost Armor, granting her Armor and Magic Resist for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Piercing Darkness
skill.desc: Senna fires a beam in the direction of her target, dealing 150% of her Attack Damage plus base damage as physical damage. For each enemy hit, she heals the lowest health ally for 60% of the damage dealt.

skill.name: Encore
skill.desc: Seraphine projects her song towards the largest group of enemy units, dealing magic damage to enemies. Allies it passes through are healed Health and gain bonus Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Unstable Concoction
skill.desc: Silco injects an unstable concoction into some of his lowest Health allies, granting them 50% maximum Health, bonus Attack Speed, and immunity to crowd control for a few seconds. When the concoction wears off, unstable units die by explosion, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies.

skill.name: Fling
skill.desc: Singed flings a nearby enemy towards the largest cluster of enemies, stunning his target for a few seconds when they land. All adjacent enemies take magic damage and are briefly stunned.

skill.name: Ricochet
skill.desc: For the next 5 seconds, Sivir grants herself bonus % Attack Speed and her attack bounce up to several times dealing 30% of her Attack Damage as physical damage to enemies hit.

skill.name: Death's Hand
skill.desc: Swain unleashes piercing bolts of eldritch power in a cone towards his target, dealing magic damage to enemies within and healing Swain for each enemy hit.

skill.name: Force of Will
skill.desc:
Syndra flings the nearest enemy towards the farthest enemy, dealing magic damage to all enemies within 1 hex upon impact and stunning the thrown target for a few seconds.

VIP Bonus: Force of Will's impact area is 1 hex larger and knocks up affected enemies for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Devour
skill.desc:
Tahm Kench devours his target, storing them in his belly and dealing magic damage over 3 seconds. During this time, they are invulnerable to other sources of damage and Tahm Kench takes 30% less damage.

If they die while inside, Tahm Kench either spits out a random component they were holding, or the cost of the unit in gold. Otherwise, he spits them towards the farthest enemy, briefly stunning targets on impact.

If a target is immune to crowd control. Tahm Kench will instead deal less magic damage.

skill.name: Blade's End
skill.desc:
Passive: Talon's 1st attack on an enemy causes them to bleed as magic damage over 7 seconds. Every 3rd attack on a target applies an additional bleed.

VIP Bonus: Talon's bleed now deals true damage and lasts 75% longer.

skill.name: Spinning Slash
skill.desc: Tryndamere spins in a line towards the most enemies, dealing physical damage to enemies in his path and empowering his next 3 attacks to deal 25% more damage.

skill.name: Piercing Bolt
skill.desc: Twitch fires a powerful bolt towards his target that pierces through enemies, deals % of his Attack Damage plus bonus physical damage, and reduces healing by 50% for 5 seconds.

skill.name: Furyhorn Storm
skill.desc: Veigar calls down Furyhorns over a few seconds near random enemies, each dealing magic damage.

skill.name: Personal Space
skill.desc:
Vex shields herself against damage over 4 seconds. When the shield expires, it deals magic damage to all enemies within 2 hexes, and an additional magic damage if it wasn't destroyed.

If it was destroyed, Personal Space becomes 15% stronger this combat. This effect can stack.

skill.name: Chaos Rays
skill.desc:
Passive: Viktor's attacks melt his target's defenses, reducing their Armor by 70% for 6 seconds.

Viktor summons multiple singularities that fire death rays, which cut across the battlefield in a line. To enemies caught in its path, death rays deal magic damage, destroy % of any remaining shields.

skill.name: Eternal Hunger
skill.desc: Passive: Warwick's Attacks deal an additional % of his target's current Health as bonus magic damage, and heal him.

skill.name: Yoink!
skill.desc: Zac stretches his arms up to 3 hexes to pull the 2 most distant enemies towards him, dealing magic damage. During this time, Zac gains 60% damage reduction.

skill.name: Lightning Crash
skill.desc:
Zeri charges herself up with electricity for 6 seconds. While electrified, she aims at the farthest enemy, her attacks pierce, and she dashes after every shot.

Passive: Zeri's Basic Attacks fire bullets, each dealing 18% of her Attack Damage as physical damage plus bonus magic damage.

VIP Bonus: Zeri's electrified duration lasts until the end of combat.

skill.name: Mini Inferno Bomb
skill.desc: Ziggs hurls a bomb at his target. After a moderate delay, the bomb lands dealing magic damage to the enemy in the epicenter, and 50% to adjacent enemies.

skill.name: Time Bomb
skill.desc: Zilean places a bomb on the closest enemy, stunning them. When the stun ends or the target dies, the bomb explodes, dealing magic damage to adjacent enemies and reducing their Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Grasping Spines
skill.desc: Zyra summons vines in the row with the most enemies, dealing magic damage and stunning them.
